name: hiMOONBIRDS
description: hiBIRDS is an ERC-20 token representing 1/1,000,000 ownership of one Moonbirds NFT in the Meta-Swap pool of Fracton Protocol. For each Moonbirds NFT added to the pool, the total supply of hiBIRDS will increase by 1 million. In contrast, for each Moonbirds NFT redeemed from the pool, the total supply of hiBIRDS will decrease by 1 million. Please note: KuCoin's hiBIRDS refers to hiMOONBIRDS on-chain.
